    You'll get access to new videos a day before the premiere
  </Tier>
  <Tier name="Fragment" price="5">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" slot="icon">
      <path
        d="M16,16l-6,0l0,-6l6,0l0,6Zm-8,2l10,0l0,-10l-10,0l0,10Z"
        style="fill-rule:nonzero;"
        class="primary"></path>
      <rect x="20" y="14" width="4" height="4" class="secondary"></rect>
      <rect x="14" y="20" width="4" height="4" class="secondary"></rect>
      <rect x="20" y="20" width="2" height="2" class="secondary"></rect>
    </svg>
    You'll get access to new videos a day before the premiere. Your name will be
    featured at the end of my videos.
  </Tier>
  <Tier name="Compute" price="10">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" slot="icon">
      <path d="M10,10l0,12l2,0l0,2l-4,0l0,-16l4,0l0,2l-2,0Z" class="primary"
      ></path>
      <rect x="20" y="22" width="4" height="2" class="secondary"></rect>
      <path d="M22,10l-2,0l0,-2l4,0l0,12l-2,0l0,-10Z" class="secondary"></path>
    </svg>
    You'll get access to new videos a day before the premiere. Your name will be
    featured at the end of my videos. You'll get exclusive access to my projects
    a month before their release.
  </Tier>
</div>

<style>
  .container {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--spacing);
  }
</style>
